{"word":"κορώνη","slug":"κορώνη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n59256\" key=\"korw/nh\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κορών-η</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, a sea-bird, possibly <sense id=\"n59256.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shearwater, Puffinus Kuhlii</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">P. anglorum</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τανύγλωσσοί τε κορῶναι εἰνάλιαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:66\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.66</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:12:418\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.418</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:593b:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">593b13</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg010:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sign.\">Sign.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:950\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">950</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:15:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEI