lScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.138</biblScope> </bibl>: generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">end, tip</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0553.tlg001:5:65\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Artem.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.65</biblScope> </bibl>: metaph., <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> infr.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0553.tlg001:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n59256.6\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">curved stern of a ship</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:345\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">345</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n59256.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tip of the plough-pole</tr_> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἱστοβοεύς</etym>), upon which the yoke is hooked or tied, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:1318\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.1318</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:1:252\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.252</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"5\" id=\"n59256.8\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">coronoid process</tr_> of the ulna, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg010.perseus-grc1:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Art.\">Art.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit